Body: Description: We're looking to create Collections for cloud-based apps and on-prem databases and wanted to know what is possible out-of-the-box and what is needed to do these type of scans.

What We've Learned Updated: Customer is asking for out of the box solutions and what their requirements are. Provided links to existing documentation.

Currently the support database types are:

  • MS SQL
  • AzureSQL
  • MongoDB
  • RedShift
  • PostgresSQL
  • Oracle
  • Db2
  • MySQL
